name: Gemma Green Photography
description: I am currently offering Photo Shoot Gift Vouchers which would make a fabulous birthday or new baby present for your loved one or as a gift to cheer up a friend or family member. I offer a FREE 1 hour sitting at my home studio in Kingsdown. All vouchers are completely open ended with no expiry date. With all vouchers ordered I will also offer a FREE mounted photo of your choice. Vouchers can be purchased for the following shoots: Newborn, child, cake smash, family and pet portrait sessions. Ordering a voucher is super easy, payment can be sent securely online and your voucher will be emailed over the same day.
